*.wasm
# The ZXing barcode-detector WASM is a build artefact of a dependency, so the
# blanket *.wasm rule above correctly keeps random .wasm generated files out.
# But the frontend ships this specific file as a public asset — the gateway
# serves it to every browser that lacks a native BarcodeDetector (Safari,
# Firefox, many Chromes). Without it, the scanner silently fails to decode
# anything the native detector can't handle, and even QR fallback through
# the polyfill is broken. Force-track this one file.
!apps/frontend/public/zxing_reader.wasm
